 Code:</strong> 114822C</p> <p class="mb--10"><strong>Duration:</strong> 2 years (full time)</p> <p class="mb--10"><strong>Intake:</strong> <a href="https://vit1.sharepoint.com/:b:/s/WebsiteDocuments/ETDP9McXibhBknT1Z9635hsB9SLFTX-1q3dCWnfJWsLFFA?e=O4VRHL" target="_blank">Refer to Intake Dates </a></p><br/><br/> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Key Facts</p> <p>The MITS degree offers core units across the complete spectrum of the IT discipline while the specialisations of our MITS course provide in-depth knowledge of a specialised area within the industry. Our MITS course includes the relevant cognitive, technical, and communication skills you will require to work successfully within the IT industry.</p> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Award</p> <p>Students who successfully complete the requirements with a specialisation as stated above will be awarded the degree “Master of Information Technology and Systems with specialisation in Software Engineering”.</p> </div>',
